            <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-indicators" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; border-top: none;">
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2" class=""></button>
                    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3" class="active" aria-current="true"></button>
                </div>

                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="~/images/Product/首頁輪播圖.jpg" alt="Taiwanese Local Farmer, Wutai Coffee Beans" class="d-block w-100" style="max-height:690px; object-fit: cover;">
                        <div>
                            <div class="carousel-caption text-start">
                                <h1>Taiwanese Local Farmer, Wutai Coffee Beans</h1>
                                <p>Locally cultivated in Wutai, Pingtung, Taiwan with dedication and heart.</p>
                                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("List","Shopping")">Buy Now</a></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="~/images/Product/pexels-daniel-reche-1556665 (1).jpg" alt="Freshly Harvested Coffee Beans" class="d-block w-100" style="max-height:690px; object-fit: cover;">
                        <div>
                            <div class="carousel-caption">
                                <h1>Freshly Harvested Coffee Beans</h1>
                                <p>Experience the rich flavor and aroma of freshly harvested coffee beans from Wutai, Pingtung.</p>
                                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("List","Shopping")">Buy Now</a></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img src="~/images/Product/首頁輪播圖3.jpg" alt="Premium Wutai Coffee" class="d-block w-100" style="max-height:690px; object-fit: cover;">
                        <div>
                            <div class="carousel-caption text-end">
                                <h1>Premium Wutai Coffee</h1>
                                <p>Indulge in the unique and premium coffee beans grown with care in Wutai, Pingtung, Taiwan.</p>
                                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("List","Shopping")">Buy Now</a></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#myCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>



            </div>

                <div class="container marketing">

                <div class="row mt-5">
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <img src="~/images/Product/台灣咖啡.jpg" alt="Taiwan Coffee" class="d-block w-100" height="300"> <!-- Updated Image Path -->
                        <h2>Taiwan</h2>
                        <p>Taiwanese coffee beans are typically high-altitude coffees, boasting complex flavors and a good balance. They often carry notes of fruit and floral scents, along with a bright acidity. Taiwan also frequently experiments with various coffee bean processing methods, including honey processing and sun-drying, imparting a diversity of flavors and unique tastes to its coffee.</p>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("List","Shopping")">Shop Now »</a></p>
                    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <img src="~/images/Product/哥倫比亞1_ixlk2u.jpg" alt="Colombian Coffee" class="d-block w-100" height="300"> <!-- Updated Image Path -->
                        <h2>Colombia</h2>
                        <p>Colombia is one of the largest coffee bean producers in the world, renowned for its balanced flavors and medium to high acidity. Colombian coffee often features nutty and chocolatey notes, coupled with a full body and a lasting aftertaste. It is a popular choice for many in the morning, offering a rich and satisfying coffee experience.</p>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("List","Shopping")">Shop Now »</a></p>
                    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <img src="~/images/Product/734104_80885.jpg" alt="Ethiopian Coffee" class="d-block w-100" height="300"> <!-- Updated Image Path -->
                        <h2>Ethiopia</h2>
                        <p>Ethiopia is the homeland of coffee, where the beans generally have a very unique and variable flavor profile. You can expect floral and citrusy aromas, along with a bright acidity and a light to medium body. Ethiopian coffee often presents a tea-like texture, and carries a very fresh and vibrant flavor, providing a stimulating and refreshing experience.</p>
                        <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="@Url.Action("List","Shopping")">Shop Now »</a></p>
                    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                </div><!-- /.row -->

                    <hr />
                <div class="row multiple-row news-grid mt-3">
                    @foreach (var post in Model)
                    {
                        <div class="row featurette mb-3">
                            <div class="col-md-7">
                                <h2 class="featurette-heading">@post.Title <span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
                                <p class="lead">
                                    @(new HtmlString(post.Content.Length > 150
                                        ? Regex.Replace(post.Content.Substring(0, Math.Min(150, post.Content.Length)), "<.*?>", string.Empty) + "..."
                                        : post.Content))            
                                </p>
                                <a href="@Url.Action("Index","Post")">
                                    Read More <span class="fa fa-arrow-right">
                                        <span class="sr-only">&nbsp;</span>
                                    </span>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-5 mt-3">
                                <img src="~/images/post/@post.PostImageUrl" alt="Image description" class="d-block w-100" height="650">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                </div>



